These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, video-games, magic-tricks, woodworking
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, lizard, turtle
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, may, march, september
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is the owner of the cat##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the ferret is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
6. the person who's birthday is in may is the owner of the lizard##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby        | magic-tricks | woodworking  | video-games | drawing  |
| Pet         | turtle    | ferret  | cat       | lizard     |
| Birthday   | march     | november | september       | may |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: lily, orchid, rose, zinnia
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, ritmeester, havana, pall-mall
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, surfing, swimming
1. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who growslily##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is between the pall-mall-smoker and the person who growszinnia##2
5. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
7. the havana-smoker is the person who's sport is surfing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Flower         | orchid | lily    | zinnia  | rose |
| Cigar   | pall-mall  | alhambra  | ritmeester   | havana    |
| Sport         | sailing | swimming | climbing | surfing      |

