.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, volleyball, rowing, biathlon
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, cooking, gardening, photography
City: colone, paris, marseilles, venice
1. the person traveling to paris is between the person traveling to venice and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
6. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
7. the person traveling to marseilles is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Sport      | volleyball | biathlon         | baseball   | rowing    |
| Hobby         | cooking | photography | collecting | gardening |
| City   | marseilles   | paris        | venice      | colone   |

