.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, cherry, blueberry, apple
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, singing, rock-climbing, fishing
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, scooter, ship
1. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the ship and the person eating apple##2
3. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
5. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating peach##1
6. the person driving the ship is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Food   | apple        | cherry   | peach | blueberry |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | video-games | singing    | fishing |
| Transport     | scooter       | bus     | ship       | car    |

