.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, cranberry, cucumber, mango
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, country, folk, metal
The people have 4 different jobs:  photographer, manager, software-developer, designer
1. the fan of metal is on the left of the manager##1
2. the person eating cherry is on the left of the software-developer##1
3. the person eating cherry is on the right of the photographer##1
4. the designer is on the left of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the fan of reggae is between the fan of metal and the software-developer##2
6. the person eating cranberry is between the person eating cherry and the person eating cucumber##2
7. the photographer is on the right of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | cucumber | cranberry  | cherry | mango      |
| Music-Genre   | folk  | metal  | reggae | country |
| Job   | designer | photographer | manager | software-developer     |

