The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, epic, mystery, spy
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, nigerian, polish, british
1. the british is the person watching epic movies##1
2. the polish is the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the japanese##1
6. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Birthday          | november  | march    | september | august  |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | spy       | epic        | drama    |
| Nationality         | nigerian | japanese | british  | polish |

