1. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is the person traveling to rome##1
3. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person traveling to colone##1
5. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is between the fonseca-smoker and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
