.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, orange, pepper, pomegranate
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, lavender, coral, ebony
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, car, snowmobile, bike
1. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1
2. the person eating pepper is on the far left##1
3. the person eating orange is between the person eating lettuce and the person who likes lavender##2
4. the person driving the car is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
5. the person who likes coral is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the car is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
7. the person driving the bike is the person who likes ebony##1
8. the person driving the subway is the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | pepper      | pomegranate | orange | lettuce |
| Color         | ebony   | lavender  | blood-red | coral |
| Transport   | bike | subway   | car | snowmobile |

