.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, biathlon, volleyball, water-polo
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, puzzles, reading
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, hot-chocolate, fanta
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person drinking fanta##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the person who's hobby is reading is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Sport    | water-polo  | volleyball | cricket | biathlon     |
| Hobby   | board-games | puzzles   | reading  | camping    |
| Beverage     | lemonade        | fanta       | iced-tea      | hot-chocolate |

