1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person who likes chestnut is the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking juice and the person who likes coral##2
4. the person who likes blue is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
7. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | juice     | almond-milk | 7up       |
| Color      | blue  | chestnut | lavender  | coral |
| Movie-Genre        | satire  | family      | time-travel        | fantasy      |

