3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person drinking water##1
5. the person drinking juice is between the person watching romance movies and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
6. the person drinking water is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking juice is the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
