2. the person who likes lavender is the person who growsamaryllis##1
3. the person who growsazalea is the security-guard##1
4. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes lilac is between the paramedic and the person who growsazalea##2
6. the project-manager is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
7. the person who likes mauve is between the person who likes lavender and the person who likes lilac##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Flower   | poppy   | lily           | azalea         | amaryllis      |
| Job     | paramedic | project-manager | security-guard | police-officer |
| Color   | fuchsia     | lilac         | mauve       | lavender        |

