2. the person playing billiard is between the person playing monopoly and the indian##2
3. the person playing monopoly is the person traveling to berlin##1
4. the person playing monopoly is between the person traveling to london and the mexican##2
5. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
6. the german is between the italian and the person traveling to miami##2
7. the person traveling to boston is the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
