4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the spanish and the argentine##2
5. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
6. the person playing canasta is between the person drinking milk and the person playing snooker##2
7. the indonesian is the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
