.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, hiking, sudoku, board-games
4 different pets are kept: bird, cat, hamster, hedgehog
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, action, horror, sports
1. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
5. the person watching sports movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the owner of the cat is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person watching horror movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby        | board-games | hiking | baking | sudoku |
| Pet         | bird       | cat     | hamster   | hedgehog   |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action | horror | sports |

 